---
title: Hearty Chicken Ragù with Linguine and Mushrooms
description: Mushrooms and chicken take this seemingly simple tomato sauce to umami town! Not only is it packed with flavour and veggies, this dinner conveniently comes together in just one pot and one pan!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragu-copieux-au-poulet-6773c594.jpg
